S. Korean people plan events to remember Kim  Il Sung
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, June 27 (KCNA) -- Members of the Thaeyang(sun) Society Active in Socho district met on June 10 to commemorate the 5th anniversary of the death of the President Kim  Il Sung, the Seoul-based radio Voice of National Salvation quoted the Seoul city committee of the National Democratic Front of South Korea as saying.
   At the meeting they set days from June 20 to July 20 for remembering President Kim  Il Sung and decided to conduct various activities during the period.   &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
